" Colorscheme for vim
" Provides easier readability with high-contrast colors
" Languages supported:
" Java, JavaScript, shell, Python, C, C++, C#, Ruby, Go, PHP, vim script, 
" Matlab, Rust, YAML, CSS, HTML, and others that have these general syntax rules
